{
  "texts": [
    "At the training time, the signal is augmented through applying SpecAugment 47 along with the addition of Gaussian noise.",
    "The output representations are mean pooled before being fed through a linear projection head.",
    "No layers are frozen and again the model is trained end-to-end.",
    "The model is fine-tuned for a total of 20 epochs.",
    "The model is evaluated on the validation set at the end of each epoch and its weights are saved."
  ]
}